    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26b.41-42_0001"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">41</fw>
                <note type="curatorial">Neihardt Collection
                    72</note>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        North St. Paul 9
                        Minnesota
                        Sept. 5, 1958
                    </dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt,</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Now that I have my two school-age children attending classes, I have found time to write to you. Hope this finds you well.</p>
                
                <p>I want you to know how much I enjoyed meeting you at the Fairmont Writer's Conference. I was happy that you were able to attend ... I realize the immensity of your bereavement though words cannot express my sympathy and my appreciation that you so willingly gave yourself and your talents to us, especially at a time like this.</p>
                
                <p>I really and truly benefited from your telling and reading of your stories. It is a
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26b.41-42_0002"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">42</fw> 
                <fw type="authorial">-2-</fw>
                
                    great thrill that I had never experienced before &#8212; to hear the stories from the lips and heart and mind of the creater-writer himself &#8212; and this one in particular. Thank you so very much.</p>
                
                <p>I try to do some writing every day. The encouragement you gave me has helped me every time I feel like quitting.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Very sincerely yours,</salute>
                    
                    <signed>Marvel Goetschel</signed>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>333 - 5th Ave. <hi rend="caps">N.E.</hi></addrLine>
                        <addrLine>North St. Paul 9.</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Minnesota</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </closer>
                
                <postscript>
                    <p>I would be pleased to hear from you.</p>
                
                    <p>Enclosed is a stamped self-addressed envelope for your convenience.</p>
                </postscript>
                      
            </div1>
        </body>
        
